
============================================
Monitor mode 
============================================
wlx00c0cab5e03d
install airmon-ng and aircrack-ng and set interface to monitor mode and up 

$ sudo apt install airmon-ng && aircrack-ng
------see wifi_driver.txt


$ airmon-ng check 

then 

$ airmon-ng check kill

$ airmon-ng start wlan0


after 

$ airmon-ng [interface] stop

$ service NetworkManager start

$ service wpa_supplicant start





